 Cordula Schacht - whose own father Hjalmar Schacht was Hitler 's minister of economics - is representing Joseph Goebbels ' estate in the case against Random House Germany and its imprint Sidler .
The dispute comes after Peter Longerich , a leading authority on the Holocaust and Nazi Germany , drew on the diaries for a biography called Goebelsels .
Now the English edition of the biography is due to be published .